<div class="flex flex-col items-center pt-10 pb-10 justify-center text-center text-[clamp(2rem,3vw,10rem)] md:text-[clamp(2rem,1.5vw,7rem)] max-w-[60vw]">
<a href="https://giftful.com/wishlists/oSAsfD5jPkNDfdshN5hh"><h1 class="font-text text-center justify-center ">Our registry is hosted </a><a class='underline hover:text-light-brown' href="https://giftful.com/wishlists/oSAsfD5jPkNDfdshN5hh">here</a>! 
<a href="https://giftful.com/wishlists/oSAsfD5jPkNDfdshN5hh">Though the wedding is on Cape Cod, please ship any gifts to our place in LA at <br><span class="text-light-brown">3185 S Sepulveda Blvd Apt 304, Los Angeles, CA 90034</span>.</a>

</h1>
